## §0. TOPOLOGICAL FOUNDATION

### Phase Space

```
U₇ ≅ ℤ/7ℤ

Phase = {⚫, ⚪, 🟡, 🟤, 🔴, 🟢, 🔵}
```

### Adjacency Law (The One Law)

```
adj(a,b) ⟺ (b - a) mod 7 ∈ {+1, -1}

|Δphase| ≡ 1 mod 7
```

**Kinematic Enforcement:** Bolts & bearings enforce neighbor-only transitions.

### Cycle Closure

```
succ⁷(p) = p
```

