## §1. GRAPH OPERATORS (C₇)

### Matrices

```
Adjacency:  A_ij = 1 iff |j - i| ≡ 1 (mod 7), else 0
Degree:     D = diag(2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2)
Laplacian:  L = D - A
```

### Dirichlet Energy

```
E_dir(ψ) = ψᵀLψ = ½ Σ_{(i,j)∈edges} (ψ_i - ψ_j)²
```

### Eigenvalue Spectrum

```
λ_k = 2(1 - cos(2πk/7)),  k ∈ {0,1,...,6}

λ₀ = 0.0000  (kernel / constant mode)
λ₁ = 0.7530  (Fiedler value)
λ₂ = 2.4450
λ₃ = 3.8019
```

