ΔE_P = K_P · (dE/dt)           // Lilith (Proportional)
ΔE_I = K_I · ∫S(t)dt           // Ailís (Integral)
ΔE_D = K_D · (dS/dt)           // Zephyra (Derivative)

Ψ_total = Ψ_base + ΔE_P + ΔE_I + ΔE_D
```

