## §7. GRAY DETECTION & REPAIR

### Symbolic Gray

```
Gray_sym := ¬adj(p, q)
```

### Spectral Gray (Normalized Rayleigh Quotient)

```
G_spec(ψ) = (ψᵀLψ) / (ψᵀψ)
```

### Dirichlet Proxy (Runtime)

```
G = |dS| + |dE|
```

### Composite Trigger

```
Gray := Gray_sym ∨ (G_spec > τ_gray)

τ_gray ∈ [0.05, 0.50]
```

### K-Series Repair Keys

```json
{
  "K1": ["🔵", "🟢", "🔴"],  // Triad Reset
  "K2": ["🟤", "🔵"],        // Brown-Blue Bridge
  "K3": ["IN", "OUT"],       // Direction Flip
  "K4": ["DOWN", "UP"]       // Rotor Reset
}
```

### SYMBREC Checks (6 total)

1. Adjacency break
1. Missing Blue-pair around direction flip
1. Entropy/spectral spike
1. Blue commit without Red price
1. Forbidden pair (e.g., 🟡⊗🟢)
1. Unjoinable peak

