## §8. UNIFIED FIELD EQUATION (UFE)

### Master PDE Form

```
λ∇²_A X - αn⁻²∂_tt X - κ∇R - γ⁻¹k_B T ln2 ∂_t X 
  - β⁻¹∇_X L - η⁻¹∇_X(∇_X S) = 0
```

### With Skip Penalty (UUE Form)

```
λ∇_A²X − α n^{-2} ∂_{tt}X − κ ∇R − γ^{-1} k_B T ln2 ∂_tX 
  − β^{-1} ∇_X L − η^{-1} ∇_X(∇_X S) + τ_adj A_skip(X) = 0
```

### Annotated Form

```
λ ∇²_A Ψ                           // Laplacian (White) — Adjacency enforcement
- α n(|Ψ|²)⁻² ∂_tt Ψ               // Refractive (Brown) — Inertia/mass
- γ⁻¹ k_B T ln 2 ∂_t Ψ             // Landauer (Red) — Information cost
- κ ∇𝒢(Ψ)                          // Repair (Black) — Gray gradient
- β⁻¹ ∇_Ψ ℒ_MDL                    // Complexity (Green) — MDL penalty
+ Ω_4°                             // Torque — Genesis gap (364° offset)
= 0
```

### Term-by-Term Physical Mapping

|Term                |Symbol         |Magick |Physical Meaning     |
|--------------------|---------------|-------|---------------------|
|Laplacian diffusion |λ∇²_A X        |⚪ White|Adjacency enforcement|
|Inertial oscillation|αn⁻²∂_tt X     |🟤 Brown|Mass/inertia (n=7)   |
|Curvature coupling  |κ∇R            |⚫ Black|Torsional geometry   |
|Information cost    |γ⁻¹kT ln2 ∂_t X|🔴 Red  |Landauer dissipation |
|Nonlinear damping   |β⁻¹∇_X L       |🟢 Green|Energy stabilization |
|Entropy feedback    |η⁻¹∇·(∇S)      |🔵 Blue |Coherence flow       |

