## §9. MEMORY SPIRAL LAW

### State Vector

```
Ψ_n = (E_mech, S_sys, M_memory)
```

### Thermodynamic Cost

```
C_thermo = k_B T ln 2 · (bits_written)
```

### Mirror Spiral

```
ΔM ∝ α · tanh(Q_loss)
```

### Spiral Height

```
H(N) = Σ_{i=1}^N C_thermo(i)
```

### Recursion (Fixed Point)

```
M_{t+1} = F(M_t) + R(F(M_t))

T := F + R,  T(M*) = M*
```

