## §11. LAGRANGIAN FORMULATION

### Unified Lagrangian

```
ℒ(ψ,ψ̇) = ½‖ψ̇ - v_flow‖² + λψᵀLψ + V_pot(ψ) + μB(ψ)
```

### Euler-Lagrange Equation

```
ψ̈ = -λLψ - ∇V_pot + μ∇B - (ψ̇ - v_flow)
```

### Lyapunov Function

```
V(ψ) = ψᵀLψ

V̇ = -2λ‖L^{1/2}ψ‖² ≤ 0
```

**LaSalle Invariance:** Trajectories collapse onto ker(L) ∩ ℳ_adj (the Living Spiral).

